## 6) Design System Plan

### A) Tokens

#### Spacing Scale
`4 / 8 / 12 / 16 / 24 / 32 / 48 / 64 / 96` px

#### Typography Scale
| Role | Size | Weight | Line Height |
|------|------|--------|-------------|
| Display / Hero | 48–72px | 900 (Black) | 1.05 |
| H1 / Page Title | 28–36px | 800 (ExtraBold) | 1.15 |
| H2 / Section | 22–28px | 700 (Bold) | 1.2 |
| H3 / Card Title | 18–20px | 700 | 1.3 |
| Body | 15–16px | 400 (Regular) | 1.5 |
| Body Bold | 15–16px | 600 (SemiBold) | 1.5 |
| Label | 13–14px | 600 | 1.4 |
| Caption / Overline | 11–12px | 700, uppercase | 1.4 |
| Monospace (numbers) | Inherits size | `tabular-nums` | — |

**Font**: Inter (already loaded). Fallback: system-ui.

#### Radii
- `xs`: 4px (chips, badges)
- `sm`: 8px (inputs, small cards)
- [md](file:///c:/Users/mzaka.ZAK-PC/Documents/Apps/LekkerLedger-1/README.md): 12px (cards, modals)
- `lg`: 16px (large cards, sheets)
- `xl`: 24px (hero CTAs, pill buttons)
- `full`: 9999px (avatars, circular)

#### Elevation (Light)
| Level | Shadow | Use |
|-------|--------|-----|
| 0 | None | Flat surfaces |
| 1 | `0 1px 2px rgba(0,0,0,.05)` | Cards, inputs |
| 2 | `0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.08)` | Dropdown, popovers |
| 3 | `0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.12)` | Modals, sheets |

#### Elevation (Dark)
Replace shadow with **surface tint**: raise background lightness by 3–5% per level, plus subtle `rgba(200,133,46,.04)` amber tint for warmth.

#### Colour Tokens (Semantic)

| Token | Light | Dark |
|-------|-------|------|
| `--bg-base` | `#faf9f7` | `#131110` |
| `--bg-surface` | `#ffffff` | `#1c1916` |
| `--bg-subtle` | `#f5f4f2` | `#252119` |
| `--bg-muted` | `#edecea` | `#2c2720` |
| `--text-primary` | `#1a1a1a` | `#ede8e1` |
| `--text-secondary` | `#525252` | `#a08e78` |
| `--text-muted` | `#737373` | `#6b5e4e` |
| `--border-default` | `#e5e5e5` | `#2c2720` |
| `--border-strong` | `#d4d4d4` | `#3d3328` |
| `--color-brand` | `#c47a1c` | `#c8852e` |
| `--color-brand-subtle` | `#fef3c7` | `rgba(200,133,46,.12)` |
| `--color-success` | `#16a34a` | `#3baa7a` |
| `--color-warning` | `#ea580c` | `#d97706` |
| `--color-error` | `#dc2626` | `#d95f5f` |
| `--color-info` | `#2563eb` | `#60a5fa` |

#### Motion
- **Duration**: 150ms (micro) / 250ms (transitions) / 400ms (enters/exits)
- **Easing**: `cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1)` (spring-like for enters), `ease-out` for exits
- **Reduced motion**: Respect `prefers-reduced-motion` — disable animations, keep opacity transitions

### B) Accessibility

- **Focus ring**: `2px solid var(--color-brand)` with `4px offset`, visible on all interactive elements
- **Contrast**: All text meets WCAG AA (4.5:1 body, 3:1 large text). Brand amber on white background needs care — use `#b45309` (darker amber) for small text on white
- **Keyboard**: Full tab navigation on web. Escape closes modals/drawers. Enter submits forms. Arrow keys navigate lists
- **Screen reader**: All icons have `aria-label`. Form errors are `aria-live="polite"`. Stepper announces step changes
- **Touch targets**: Minimum 48×48dp on Android, 44×44px on web
- **Large text**: Support `font-size` scaling up to 200% without layout breaking

### C) Component Inventory (Summary)

> **Full spec offloaded to AI Coder #2** — see paste-ready prompt below.

**Minimum set** (30 components):

| Category | Components |
|----------|-----------|
| **Actions** | Button (Primary/Secondary/Ghost/Danger × default/hover/active/focus/disabled/loading), IconButton, FAB (Android) |
| **Forms** | Input (text/number/date/currency), Select, Switch, Checkbox, Radio, DatePicker, Label, HelperText, ErrorText, FormGroup |
| **Layout** | Card, Divider, Container, Grid, Stack, Spacer |
| **Navigation** | Sidebar, BottomNav, TabBar, Breadcrumb, SideDrawer, TopAppBar |
| **Data** | Table (web), ListItem (mobile), StatCard, Badge, Tag/Chip, Avatar, EmptyState, Skeleton, Pagination |
| **Feedback** | Toast, Alert/Banner, Dialog/Modal, BottomSheet (mobile), Tooltip, ProgressBar |
| **Composite** | Stepper/Wizard, FilterBar, SearchInput, DocumentPreview, ShareSheet, ConfirmDialog |

**Platform differences:**
- **Table → ListCard**: Desktop shows data tables with sortable columns. Mobile shows card lists with key info.
- **Modal → BottomSheet**: Desktop modals are centred overlays. Mobile/Android actions use bottom sheets.
- **Sidebar → BottomNav**: Desktop has persistent sidebar. Android has bottom navigation.

