## 7) Interaction Patterns

### Validation & Compliance Guardrails

| Pattern | When | Behaviour |
|---------|------|-----------|
| **Inline field validation** | On blur | Error text appears below input. Input border turns red. Error clears on valid input |
| **Cross-field validation** | On "Next" step / submit | e.g., "Ordinary hours ÷ days worked ≠ expected hours/day" — shown as a warning banner at top of step |
| **Blocking error** | Before save | Review screen highlights errors in red. "Save & Preview" button disabled until resolved |
| **Non-blocking warning** | Before save | Amber warning with "I understand, proceed anyway" checkbox. e.g., "Rate is exactly NMW — consider if this is correct" |
| **Compliance checklist** | On payslip preview | Green checks / amber warnings for: employer details present, rate ≥ NMW, UIF correctly applied, hours within BCEA limits, leave recorded. Each item links to "fix it" |
| **Minimum wage block** | On rate input | If rate < NMW: red error, field resets to NMW, explanation shown. Cannot proceed |

### Filtering / Sorting / Search

- **URL-synced filters** (web): Filters are reflected in URL params (`?period=2026-03&employee=abc`). Page refresh preserves state.
- **State-persistent filters** (Android): Stored in local state, cleared on back navigation.
- **Employee search**: Fuzzy search by name. Debounced 300ms. Results highlight matching text.
- **Payslip history filters**: By employee, by period (month/year picker), by status (generated/draft).
- **Sort**: Column header click on desktop tables. Dropdown selector on mobile.

### Empty / Loading / Error States

| State | Visual |
|-------|--------|
| **Empty (first time)** | Illustration + welcoming copy + single primary CTA ("Add your first employee") |
| **Empty (filtered)** | "No results match your filters" + "Clear filters" link |
| **Loading** | Skeleton placeholders matching the layout structure (not a fullscreen spinner) |
| **Error (recoverable)** | Amber banner with error description + "Try again" button |
| **Error (critical)** | Red banner with "Contact support" link. Error boundary catches crashes with friendly message |
| **Offline** | Grey banner: "You're offline — changes will sync when connected" + amber dot on sync icon |

### Bulk Actions

- Available on: Payslip generation (run month for all employees), Leave import
- **Flow**: Select all → Review confirmation screen showing each affected item → Confirm → Progress indicator → Toast on completion
- **Undo**: Bulk payslip generation shows "Undo (30s)" toast. After timeout, records are permanent.
- **No bulk delete**: Destructive bulk actions require individual confirmation (safety first for payroll data).

### Performance

- **Virtual scrolling**: Employee lists > 20 items, payslip history > 50 items
- **Lazy loading**: Calculator, PDF preview, charts loaded on demand (dynamic import)
- **Skeleton loading**: All data-dependent screens show skeleton within 100ms of navigation
- **IndexedDB**: Current approach is correct. No change needed.
- **Image optimization**: Use `next/image` everywhere (side drawer currently uses `<img>`)

