## Extra Considerations

### Offline / Low-Data Mode
- Cache last pay run + all employee profiles in IndexedDB (already done via localforage)
- Queue edits with `pendingSync` flag, process on reconnect
- Show "Last synced: 2 hours ago" in sidebar footer + amber dot if stale (> 24h)
- All PDF generation works offline (pdf-lib is client-side)

### WhatsApp-Friendly Sharing
- "Share" button on payslip preview → opens native share sheet
- Options: "Share PDF" (full document) or "Share Summary" (text-only with key numbers)
- Privacy control: "Include employee ID?" toggle before sharing
- WhatsApp deep link: `https://wa.me/?text=...` with URL-encoded summary

### South Africa Localisation
- **Currency**: Always `R X,XXX.XX` format (space between R and number, comma for thousands, dot for decimals)
- **Dates**: `DD MMM YYYY` (e.g., "03 Mar 2026") — SA convention
- **Public holidays**: Full 2026 SA holiday calendar built in. Auto-detect holidays in pay period.
- **Language tone**: Plain English, conversational, no legalese. "This is required by law" not "In terms of BCEA Section 29(1)(a)..."
- **Future**: Add Afrikaans + isiZulu UI translations as a Phase 5 milestone

### Trust & Audit
- **Change log per entity**: Every employee, payslip, contract gets a `changeLog: { timestamp, field, oldValue, newValue }[]` array
- **History screen**: Shows timeline of changes with "What changed" diffs
- **Exportable audit log**: "Download full audit trail" button → generates a PDF with all changes
- **Record retention notice**: "BCEA requires 3 years of payslip records" info panel on history screen

### Document Quality
- **PDF**: Continue using pdf-lib for client-side generation. Template-based with A4 dimensions (210×297mm)
- **Typography**: Use embedded fonts (not system fonts) in PDFs for consistency across devices
- **Print margins**: 15mm all sides (SA standard business document)
- **Signatures**: "Employer signature" and "Employee acceptance" fields. Digital acceptance tracking (date + name)

### Guided Compliance Guardrails
- **Per payslip**: Compliance checklist on review step (employer details ✅, rate ≥ NMW ✅, UIF applied ✅, hours within BCEA ✅)
- **Per contract**: Required clauses checklist (job description ✅, hours ✅, rate ✅, leave ✅, notice period ✅)
- **Per employee**: Status dashboard (contract current? ✅, leave balance OK? ⚠️, all payslips generated? ✅)
- Each item links to "Fix it" → navigates to the relevant edit screen

### Error-Proofing
- **Smart defaults**: Pay period auto-fills to current month. Ordinary hours = days worked × hours/day. UIF auto-calculates.
- **Review screen**: Read-only summary before generating payslip. Every field editable via "change" link.
- **Undo**: After generating a payslip, 30-second "Undo" toast. After that, payslip is permanent (but can be "voided" with a reason).
- **Duplicate detection**: Warn if generating a payslip for the same employee + period that already exists.

### Security & Privacy
- **App lock**: Support Android biometric lock via TWA
- **PII masking**: In list views, show `J*** D***` for employee names if "privacy mode" is enabled
- **Secure storage**: IndexedDB data is device-local. No server transmission. POPIA-compliant by architecture.
- **Export security**: PDFs include a "Generated by LekkerLedger" watermark with generation timestamp (audit trail)

### Multi-Employee Scalability
- **Bulk payslip generation**: "Run month" button generates payslips for all employees using last month's template, with individual override
- **Filterable history**: Filter payslips by employee, period, or status
- **Employee groups**: Future feature — group employees by type (domestic worker, gardener, au pair) for different default settings
- **Performance**: Virtual scrolling for lists > 20 employees. Lazy-load payslip history.

### Notifications & Reminders
- **Pay day reminder**: "It's the 25th — time to run payslips" (configurable day)
- **Contract renewal**: "Thandi's contract expires in 30 days — review now"
- **Missing hours**: "You haven't captured hours for March 2026 yet"
- **Leave balance**: "Sipho has 2 leave days remaining this year"
- **Implementation**: Use web notifications (with permission) + in-app banner on dashboard

### Accessibility
- **Large text**: Support browser font-size scaling up to 200% without layout breaking. Test at `font-size: 24px` on body.
- **High contrast**: Offer "High Contrast" toggle in settings → increases all border/text contrast to WCAG AAA
- **Touch targets**: Minimum 48×48dp on Android, 44×44px on web. Current violations: employee action icon buttons (32px) — fixed in Phase 2
- **Focus management**: Visible focus ring on all interactive elements. Skip-to-content link on web.
- **Keyboard navigation**: Full tab order. Enter submits. Escape closes. Arrow keys navigate.
- **Screen reader**: All icons have `aria-label`. Dynamic content uses `aria-live`. All images have `alt` text.
